<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>{{ title }}</title>
    <link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lato:100,300,400,700,900,100italic,300italic,400italic,700italic,900italic' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css'/>
    {{#newrelic}}
        {{{ newrelic.getBrowserTimingHeader }}}
    {{/newrelic}}
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/2.1.3/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-default navbar-fixed-top">
      <div class="navbar-header">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">
            <img id = "company-logo" src="images/logo.png">
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="navbar-padding-right">
        <ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right">
           <li>
               <p class="navbar-btn">
                   <a href="/login" class="btn custom-button" id="login-btn-navbar">Log In</a>
               </p>
           </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </nav>
    <!-- start of outer container -->
    <div class="container-fluid container-margin-landing landing-pic">
        <div class="row" id="first-section">
            <div id="intro" class="col-xs-7">
                <h1 class="heading bold text-center">The old rules of waiting are over.</h3>
                <p class="text-center info-text"> Let us help you revolutionize your patient waiting experience with effortless check-in, form management, arrival notification, and appointment integration for your office.</p>
                <form class="form-group" action="" method="post">
                    <div class="col-xs-9">
                        <input type="company" class="small form-control" id="companyName" name="companyName" value="{{companyName}}" method="post" placeholder="Step 1: Enter company name">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xs-1 text-small">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn custom-button">Sign Up</button>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>

            <div class="col-xs-4 ">
                <img id="intro-image" src="images/ipad.png">
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row" id="second-section">
            <div class="col-xs-6">
                <div>
                    <blockquote class="testimonial">
                        <p>With a limited budget and tight schedule, this check-in app really saved me time and cost to run the dental clinic I just opened up. Thank you, iReceptionist. You’re a life-saver.</p>
                    </blockquote>
                    <div class="arrow-down"></div>
                    <img src="images/jennifer.jpg" class="testimonial-image">
                    <span class="testimonial-author">Dr. Jennifer Kim, DDS | <span>San Francisco, California</span></span>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <blockquote class="testimonial testimonial-grey">
                        <p>Wow! iReceptionist was the perfect addition to our offices! It’s elegant, fast, and our customers absolutely love it! The team’s continued support and commitment to excellence has made me a life-long customer. Definitely the GOLD standard for check-in apps!</p>
                    </blockquote>
                    <div class="arrow-down arrow-down-grey"></div>
                    <img src="images/leonard.jpg" class="testimonial-image">
                    <span class="testimonial-author">Dr. Leonard McCoy, M.D. | <span>Riverside, California</span></span>
                    
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xs-6">
                <div>
                    <blockquote class="testimonial testimonial-grey">
                        <p>iReceptionist is truly an aesthetic experience, I love how intuitive and modern the design is. Making appointments and checking in has never been easier.</p>
                    </blockquote>
                    <div class="arrow-down arrow-down-grey"></div>
                    <img src="images/betty.jpg" class="testimonial-image">
                    <span class="testimonial-author">Betty Johnson | <span>Stockholm, Sweden</span></span>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <blockquote class="testimonial">
                        <p>I can’t believe how much time I saved using iReceptionist. It was truly a breathe of fresh air. Never again will I have to deal with the hassle of a grumpy receptionist and a clipboard!</p>
                    </blockquote>
                    <div class="arrow-down"></div>
                    <img src="images/joel.jpg" class="testimonial-image">
                    <span class="testimonial-author">Joel Spolsky | <span>Kathmandu, Nepal</span></span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <footer class="footer navbar-bottom">
        <div class="container">
            <ul class="list-inline footer-links text-center">
                <!--<li><a href="">About Us</a></li>
                <li><a href="">Store</a></li>
                <li><a href="">Jobs</a></li>
                <li><a href="">Privacy</a></li>
                <li><a href="">Terms</a></li>
                <li><a href="">Support</a></li>-->
                <li class = "footer-copyright">Copyright &#169; Gold Team-CSE 112, Winter 2015. All Rights Reserved.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
